{[%mdl 8192] B48: Sicilian: Taimanov: 5 Nc3 Qc7 6 Be3 a6 without Be2} 1. e4 c5
2. Nf3 e6 3. d4 cxd4 4. Nxd4 Nc6 5. Be3 Qc7 6. Nc3 a6 7. a3 Nf6 8. Be2 Be7 9.
O-O O-O 10. h3 $146 {Consolidates g4} (10. Nb3 b5 11. f4 d6 12. Bf3 Bb7 13. Qe1
(13. g4 Rfe8 14. g5 Nd7 15. Qe2 Bf8 16. Rad1 g6 17. Qf2 b4 18. axb4 Nxb4 19.
Rd4 Nc6 20. Rc4 Rac8 21. Rd1 Qd8 22. Ra1 Nce5 23. Rxc8 Nxf3+ 24. Qxf3 Qxc8 25.
Rd1 f5 26. gxf6 Nxf6 27. Nd2 Bg7 {Sinprayoon,P (2240)-Izquierdo,D (2270)
Thessaloniki 1988 1/2-1/2 (65)}) 13... b4 14. axb4 Nxb4 15. Qf2 d5 16. e5 Ne4
17. Bxe4 dxe4 18. Bb6 Qc8 19. Rae1 a5 20. Re3 a4 21. Nd4 Ra6 22. f5 f6 23. Nxa4
Rxa4 24. Nxe6 Nd5 {Trejbal,D (2200)-Banas,J (2350) Stary Smokovec 1976 0-1 (36)
}) (10. Kh1 Ne5 (10... Rd8 11. f4 d6 12. Qe1 Bd7 13. Qg3 b5 14. e5 Ne8 15. Ne4
Rac8 16. Bd3 g6 17. Nf3 dxe5 18. fxe5 Ng7 19. Bg5 Nh5 20. Qh4 Bxg5 21. Qxg5 f5
22. exf6 Qf4 23. g4 e5 24. gxh5 Bf5 25. f7+ {Ibragimov,A (2250)-Yandemirov,V 
(2500) Ekaterinburg 1997 1-0 (33)}) 11. f4 Nc4 12. Bc1 d6 13. Qd3 b5 14. Ndxb5
axb5 15. Nxb5 Qa5 16. Qxc4 Ba6 17. a4 Rfc8 18. Qd4 d5 19. Bd2 Qd8 20. exd5 Rxc2
21. d6 Bxd6 22. Bf3 Nd5 23. Bxd5 exd5 24. Bc3 Bf8 {Aleskerov,F (2314)-Kovalyov,
A (2616) Greensboro 2015 1/2-1/2 (35)}) (10. f4 d5 11. exd5 exd5 $11) 10... b5
$11 11. Re1 Bb7 12. Bf1 Rac8 13. Rc1 (13. Bd3 Ne5 $11) 13... Rfd8 14. Qe2 (14.
Bd3 d5 15. exd5 Nxd5 16. Nxd5 Rxd5 17. Nxc6 Qxc6 $15) 14... Na5 (14... Nxd4 15.
Bxd4 e5 16. Nd5 Nxd5 17. exd5 $15) 15. Qd2 {White has an active position} (15.
Bg5 h6 16. Bh4 Qb6 $15) 15... Bxa3 (15... d5 16. Ncxb5 axb5 17. Nxb5 $15) 16.
Bf4 {White threatens to win material: Bf4xc7} (16. Ndxb5 axb5 17. Nxb5 Nc4 18.
Bxc4 Qxc4 19. Nxa3 Qxe4 $11) 16... Qc5 17. Nd1 (17. bxa3 $5 {might be a viable
alternative} Qxc3 18. Qxc3 Rxc3 19. a4 bxa4 20. Bd2 $11) 17... e5 $17 18. Bxe5
Bb4 (18... Qxe5 19. bxa3 Nxe4 20. Qxa5 Qxd4 21. Qb4 $17) 19. c3 Qxe5 20. cxb4
Rxc1 21. Qxc1 Qxd4 22. bxa5 Rc8 (22... Nxe4 $2 {doesn't lead to the expected
results} 23. Qc7 Rf8 24. Qxb7 $18) 23. Qf4 (23. Qe3 Qxe4 24. Qxe4 Bxe4 $17)
23... Qb4 24. Nc3 (24. Qe3 Bxe4 25. Nc3 Bc6 $17) 24... Qxb2 $19 25. Nd5 Bxd5 ({
Inferior is} 25... Nxd5 26. exd5 g6 27. Qd6 $17) 26. exd5 Qc3 (26... Nxd5 27.
Qd6 Qc3 28. Qxa6 $16) 27. Re3 Qxa5 28. Rg3 $4 {but even a better move would
not have saved the game} (28. Qd6 h6 29. g3 $19) 28... Nh5 29. Rxg7+ (29. Qd6 {
does not improve anything} Nxg3 30. fxg3 g6 $19) 29... Nxg7 30. Qg5 (30. g4 {
doesn't change anything anymore} b4 31. Qe4 b3 $19) 30... Qd8 (30... Qe1 {
keeps an even firmer grip} 31. Qg3 $19) 31. Qg4 (31. Qh6 {cannot undo what has
already been done} d6 $19) 31... Rc5 (31... Rc1 $142 $5 {seems even better} 32.
g3 Qe7 33. Kg2 $19) 32. d6 (32. g3 {is not much help} Rxd5 33. Qe4 Qg5 $19)
32... a5 33. h4 (33. Bd3 {doesn't change the outcome of the game} a4 $19) 33...
Kh8 (33... a4 $142 $5 {and Black can already relax} 34. Qd4 Qb6 35. Qe3 $19)
34. Qf3 Rf5 (34... Nf5 $142 {might be the shorter path} 35. Qh5 Qf6 36. g3 $19)
35. Qh3 (35. Qe4 {doesn't do any good} Qe8 36. Qb1 Re5 $19) 35... Rh5 (35...
Qb6 $142 {and the rest is a matter of technique} 36. Qg3 a4 37. Bd3 $19) 36. g3
Ne6 37. Qg4 Rc5 38. h5 (38. Qf3 {is not the saving move} Qe8 $19) 38... Qg5 39.
Qf3 Kg7 40. g4 Qd5 41. Qg3 b4 42. Bd3 Rc1+ 43. Kh2 (43. Bf1 {doesn't get the
cat off the tree} Nd4 44. Qd3 Nf3+ 45. Kg2 Ne1+ 46. Kh3 Nxd3 47. Bg2 Nxf2+ 48.
Kg3 Qe5+ 49. Kxf2 Qf4+ 50. Bf3 Rc2+ 51. Ke1 Qd2+ 52. Kf1 Qf2#) 43... Qh1# (
43... Rh1#) 0-1

