$142 {and White has reached his goal} e4 22. fxe6 Qe8 23. Qxe8 Rxe8 24. Bxe4
Bf8 $18) 21... Kg8 22. Nxf8 Qxf8 23. Nb4 Bf7 (23... Qf7 {is the last straw} 24.
Qxf7+ Kxf7 25. exf5 Bb3 26. Rc7+ Kf6 $18) 24. Qxf5 Qe8 25. Rc8 Bg6 (25... Bf6 {
does not win a prize} 26. Rxe8+ Bxe8 27. Qxf6 h5 28. Ra1 Rb1+ 29. Bxb1 Kh7 30.
Ra7+ Bf7 31. Rxf7+ Kg8 32. Qg7#) 26. Rxe8+ Bxe8 27. Nd5 (27. Bc4+ d5 28. Bxd5+
