{[%mdl 8192] E07: Closed Catalan: Main Line (5 Nf3 0-0 6 0-0 Nbd7)} 1. d4 d5 2.
c4 e6 3. Nf3 Nf6 4. g3 Be7 5. Bg2 Nbd7 (5... c6 6. O-O (6. Qc2 Nbd7 7. Nbd2 b6
8. e4 O-O 9. e5 Ne8 10. h4 h6 11. O-O Ba6 12. Re1 Rc8 13. b3 c5 14. dxc5 Bxc5
15. Qd1 Nc7 16. a3 dxc4 17. Nxc4 Nb8 18. Nd6 Bxd6 19. exd6 Nd5 20. Bb2 Rc6 {
Ghaem Maghami,E (2609)-Xu,Y (2463) Al Ain 2015 1/2-1/2 (40)}) 6... Nbd7 7. Qc2
(7. Nbd2 O-O 8. Re1 Re8 9. e4 dxe4 10. Nxe4 Nxe4 11. Rxe4 Bf6 12. Qe2 Qa5 13.
Bd2 Qa6 14. Re3 Qb6 15. b4 Qc7 16. Rc1 Nf8 17. Re4 Bd7 18. Ne5 Bxe5 19. Rxe5
Ng6 20. Re3 Rac8 21. a4 a6 {Nabavi,P (2228)-Malachowski,M (2173) Germany 2010
1/2-1/2 (54)}) (7. b3 Ne4 8. Nfd2 Nxd2 9. Qxd2 O-O 10. Nc3 dxc4 11. bxc4 c5 12.
d5 Nb6 13. Qd3 Bf6 14. Rb1 Bd7 15. Ne4 exd5 16. Nxf6+ Qxf6 17. cxd5 Rad8 18.
Qa3 Rfe8 19. e4 a6 20. Bb2 Qg6 21. Qxc5 Bb5 {Hirn,O (2235)-Ponnath,L (2275)
Heroldsbach 1997 1-0 (36)}) 7... b6 8. Rd1 Ba6 9. b3 Rc8 10. Nbd2 c5 11. e4
cxd4 12. exd5 exd5 13. Nxd4 O-O 14. Nf1 b5 15. Ne3 bxc4 16. Nxd5 Nxd5 17. Bxd5
cxb3 18. Qxb3 Nc5 19. Qf3 Bf6 20. Rb1 {Harikrishna,P (2665)-Vocaturo,D (2545)
Wijk aan Zee 2012 1-0}) 6. Nbd2 $146 (6. O-O Ne4 7. Qc2 f5 8. b3 O-O 9. Ne1 Bf6
10. Bb2 c6 11. Nd3 Qe8 12. Nd2 b5 13. cxd5 cxd5 14. Nf3 a5 15. Rfc1 Ba6 16. Qc6
Qe7 17. Qc2 Rfc8 18. Qd1 b4 19. a3 Rxc1 20. Qxc1 Rc8 {Abdelnabbi,I (2414)-Adly,
A (2315) Cairo 2003 0-1 (54)}) 6... h6 {Prevents intrusion on g5} 7. Qc2 O-O 8.
O-O Re8 9. Re1 (9. e4 Nxe4 10. Nxe4 dxe4 11. Qxe4 Rb8 $14) 9... c6 (9... c5 10.
b3 $11) 10. b3 Bd6 11. Bb2 a5 12. Ne5 Nf8 (12... a4 $5 $14) 13. e4 $16 Bb4 14.
Bc3 Bxc3 15. Qxc3 dxe4 16. Nxe4 Nxe4 17. Bxe4 Qc7 18. Qf3 (18. c5 Nh7 $16)
18... Rd8 19. Rad1 $4 {throwing away the advantage} (19. Qe3 f6 20. Nf3 Bd7 $16
) 19... Rb8 $4 {weakening the position} (19... f6 $142 $17) 20. c5 $16 f6 (
20... f5 21. Bc2 $16) 21. Nc4 Bd7 22. h4 Be8 23. Bd3 Bf7 24. Nd6 (24. Qe3 Nd7
$16) 24... Rd7 25. Re3 b5 $2 (25... Rbd8 $142 $5 $16) 26. Be4 $18 Rb6 $4 {
the pressure is too much, Black crumbles} (26... Rbd8 $18) 27. Nxf7 Ra6 28. Nd6
Rxd6 (28... f5 {doesn't improve anything} 29. Bc2 $18) 29. cxd6 Qxd6 30. Rc3
Qa3 (30... b4 {is no salvation} 31. Rc2 $18) 31. Bxc6 Qxa2 (31... Qd6 {cannot
change what is in store for White} 32. d5 e5 33. Bxb5 $18) 32. Bxb5 (32. d5
$142 {keeps an even firmer grip} Qa3 33. dxe6 Qe7 34. Bxb5 Rb6 $18) 32... Rb6
33. Bc4 Qb2 (33... Qa3 {hardly improves anything} 34. d5 Qe7 35. dxe6 $18) 34.
Re3 (34. d5 Qxc3 35. Qxc3 e5 36. d6+ Kh8 37. d7 Nxd7 38. Rxd7 Kh7 39. Bd3+ f5
40. Bxf5+ Rg6 41. Qxe5 Kg8 42. Bxg6 a4 43. Qxg7#) 34... Qc2 35. Qe2 (35. d5 Rd6
36. Rc3 Qxd1+ 37. Qxd1 e5 $18) 35... Qf5 (35... Qxe2 {the only chance to get
some counterplay} 36. Rxe2 Rd6 $18) 36. g4 Qf4 37. Re4 (37. d5 Kf7 38. dxe6+
Ke7 39. Red3 Qe5 40. Qd2 f5 41. Rd7+ Kf6 42. Rf7+ Kg6 43. e7 Rb8 44. exf8=N+
Rxf8 45. Qd6+ Kh7 46. Qxe5 Rxf7 47. Bxf7 fxg4 48. Rd8 g3 49. Qe4+ g6 50. Qxg6#)
37... Qd6 38. Ra1 (38. Re1 $142 {makes it even easier for White} Rb8 39. h5 Kh7
$18) 38... Kf7 (38... Kh7 {does not solve anything} 39. Rxa5 Rb8 40. h5 $18)
39. Rxa5 Ng6 40. Ra7+ Ne7 41. Kg2 Kg6 (41... Ke8 {does not help much} 42. Rxe6
Qxe6 43. Bxe6 Rxe6 44. Qxe6 Kf8 45. Qxe7+ Kg8 46. Qxg7#) 42. Rxe6 (42. Rxe6
Qc6+ 43. Rxc6 h5 44. Qe4+ Nf5 45. Qxf5+ Kh6 46. Qxh5#) 1-0

