{[%mdl 8256] C97: Closed Ruy Lopez: Chigorin Defence: 11 d4 Qc7, sidelines} 1.
e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Bb5 a6 4. Ba4 Nf6 5. O-O Be7 6. Re1 b5 7. Bb3 d6 8. h3 O-O
