$2 24. Rxf6 gxf6 25. Qf3 $18) 24. fxg7 Bxg7 $16) 22... Nxf3+ (22... Bc6 $5 23.
bxc5 Bxe4 24. cxd6 Qc6 25. Nxe5 Bxe5 $11) 23. gxf3 $14 Rc8 24. Kh1 c4 {This
push gains space} (24... Rfd8 $5 $14) 25. Rg1 $16 Kh7 26. Bd4 (26. Bb6 $142 $5
Qb7 27. Rxd6 $16) 26... Be5 $11 27. f4 {White threatens to win material: f4xe5}
Bc6 $4 {throwing away the advantage} (27... Bxd4 $142 {the only rescuing move}
28. Qxd4 f6 $11) 28. fxe5 $18 Bxe4+ 29. Kh2 dxe5 30. Qg3 $4 {what a pity,
victory was in sight} (30. Be3 Rg8 $18) 30... f6 (30... exd4 $142 {and Black
has reached his goal} 31. Bb1 Rfd8 $19) 31. Qg6+ $18 Kh8 32. Bc5 (32. Bb6 Qf7
33. Bb1 Qxg6 34. fxg6 Rce8 $18) 32... Rfe8 (32... Rg8 $142 $5 33. c3 Bf3 $16)
33. Rd6 Rcd8 $4 {the final mistake, not that it matters anymore} (33... Red8
34. Bb6 Rxd6 35. Bxc7 Rd2+ 36. Kg3 Rxc7 $18) 34. Bb6 $1 {Mate threat} (34. Bb6
Bxf5 35. Qxe8+ (35. Qxf5 $6 Qxd6 36. Bxd8 e4+ 37. Kh1 Qxd8 $11) 35... Rxe8 36.
Bxc7 Bxc2 37. Rxa6 $18) 1-0

